hands_on_practices.solution:
1. 光子数密度
$$n_\gamma=\frac{2\,\zeta(3)}{\pi^2}\Bigl(\frac{k_B T}{\hbar c}\Bigr)^3$$
2. 净电子密度
$$n_{e^-}-n_{e^+}=\eta_L\,n_\gamma$$
3. 物质势
$$V=\sqrt2\,G_F\,(n_{e^-}-n_{e^+})
=\sqrt2\,G_F\,\eta_L\,\frac{2\,\zeta(3)}{\pi^2}\Bigl(\frac{k_B T}{\hbar c}\Bigr)^3$$
4. 真空振荡频率
$$\omega_{vac}=\frac{\Delta m^2\,c^4}{2E_\nu}
=\frac{\Delta m^2\,c^4}{2\,\alpha\,k_B T}$$
5. 令 $V=\omega_{vac}$ 并设 $x=k_B T$：
$$\sqrt2\,G_F\,\eta_L\,\frac{2\,\zeta(3)}{\pi^2}\frac{x^3}{(\hbar c)^3}
=\frac{\Delta m^2\,c^4}{2\,\alpha\,x}$$
6. 整理得到 $x^4$：
$$x^4=\frac{\Delta m^2\,c^4\,(\hbar c)^3\,\pi^2}
{4\,\alpha\,\sqrt2\,\zeta(3)\,G_F\,\eta_L}$$
7. 因此
$$k_B T_{osc}
=x
=\left[\frac{\pi^2\,\Delta m^2\,c^4\,(\hbar c)^3}
{4\,\alpha\,\sqrt2\,\zeta(3)\,G_F\,\eta_L}\right]^{1/4}
=\left[\frac{\pi^2\,\Delta m^2\,\hbar^3c^7}
{4\,\sqrt2\,\alpha\,\zeta(3)\,G_F\,\eta_L}\right]^{1/4}.$$
